headline: The Cooper Companies (COO) Q3 Earnings Preview: What You Should Know Beyond the Headline Estimates
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for The Cooper Companies (COO), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended July 2025.
